it.unibz.krdb.obda.owlrefplatform.core.queryevaluation

Interface EvaluationEngine

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    JDBCEngine

    public interface EvaluationEngine
    An interface representing the Evaluation engine for a Technique wrapper. The main task of such an evaluation engine is to evaluate the rewritten and unfolded data log program over the data source.
    Author:
    Manfred Gerstgrasser
